</head>
  <div class="container-fluid">
    <h1>G2 Crowd Team Roster</h1>
      <hr>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-body">
        <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
          
          <% @engineers.each do |engineer| %>
            <h3><%= engineer.name %></h3>
              <br>
              <% engineer.image_url %>
              
              #image data exists on the backend, but I have not styled the page to display it yet. That is why it is present, but undisplayed in this loop.

            <h5><%= engineer.title %></h5>
              <br>
            <article><%= engineer.bio %></article>
              <br>
              <strong><text>Want to work with <%= engineer.name %>?</text></strong>

              <svg id="icon-thumbs-up" type="image/svg+xml" data="thumbs-up.svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512" width="40" height="20">
